description:
Everyone who has the Spirit can have the fruits of the Spirit, but can everyone have spiritual gifts? Frank Hasel shares how everyone can have spiritual gifts, but not everyone has the same spiritual gifts. 

Find the full video about the 17th Fundamental Belief, ‘Spiritual Gifts and Ministries” here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SiUakyrqIH8
